# Controls what gets uploaded to Cloud Build for `gcloud run deploy --source`.
# Defined explicitly so gcloud does NOT fall back to the repo .gitignore —
# the demo video (landing/assets/videos/demo.mp4) is gitignored but MUST ship
# in the Cloud Run image.
#
# Ship only the web-encoded demo.mp4 from the videos dir; exclude the large
# HEVC source master (and any other raw clips) so they don't bloat the image.
#
# Note: Dockerfile and .dockerignore are intentionally NOT excluded — Cloud
# Build needs the Dockerfile, and .dockerignore keeps it out of the served
# HTML at image-build time.
.DS_Store
assets/videos/*
!assets/videos/demo.mp4

# scripts/ holds dev tooling (e.g. build-llms-full.py) — the generated
# llms-full.txt ships, the script itself doesn't need to.
scripts/
